snippet.title: Mega Cat Studios Collection 2 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured directly from the Original Evercade. All but one of the 8 games in this cart are Mega Drive / Genesis games.

Games:
00:08 - Alter Ego: Dreamwalker
03:20 - Arkagis Revolution
13:38 - Devwill Too MD
16:48 - Gluf
20:06 - Misplaced
25:00 - Romeow and Julicat
28:05 - Roniu's Tale [The only NES game on this cart]
33:09 - Yazzie
